Package: nightlight
Type: Package
Title: R package for working with NOAA night light data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Altaf Ali <altaf@fastmail.com>
Maintainer: Who to complain to <yourfault@somewhere.net>
Description: R package for working with satellite composites from National
    Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA). We use the cleaned up dataset
    from NOAA that excludes cloud cover and ephemeral events. Sunlit data, moonlit
    data, and glare are also excluded.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: RCurl,
 R.utils,
 raster,
 stringr,
 dplyr